snippet.title: The SS Destiny Disaster Steam V3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the new and very improved demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3197230/The_SS_Destiny_Disaster/

Humanity's ambition for the stars turns into a brutal fight for survival. The crew of The SS Destiny discovers a bacteria that turns their mission into a nightmare. Find resources, battle infected, and escape the doomed ship as it spirals into chaos. 

Any feedback is greatly appreciated!
